commit.message:
feat(pd): grants updates;

- Conditional requirements for a bunch of fields.
- Conditional formatting for some fields.

feat(pd): grants cont;

- More grants changes.
- Added french translations.

feat(pd): grants cont;

- More grants changes.
- Added french translations.

fix(pd): formatting, changelog;

- Added more changes to log file.
- Fixed field description formatting.

feat(pd): template warning;

- Add template warning for Grants.
- Update template date to December 1st.

